#. type: textblock
#: po4a:35 po4a-gettextize:25 po4a-normalize:11 po4a-translate:27
#: po4a-updatepo:21
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Extra option(s) to pass to the format plugin. Specify each option in the "
